---
title: Roasted Salmon and Lemon-Dill Risotto with Peas and Creamy Sauce
description: This risotto dish checks all the boxes! Tender salmon sits atop savoury risotto dotted with peas and enhanced by a touch of lemon and dill. A creamy lemon-dill sauce adds some luxury this memorable dinner that's ready in just 20 minutes!
